lled the exponent $\\tau^*$ of SPT. We prove\nthat the results are the same for both classes $\\Lambda$, and obtain conditions\nfor WT, PT, SPT with and without EXP and UEXP.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Nov 2012 23:46:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-27"}
